</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_349" id="174r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_349_r1l7">Heincʒ von Gich cʒu Melſendorff </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_349_r1l8"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan> / vns hat fürgelegt / Heincʒ Spörlein <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> / vvie Jr </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_349_r1l9">Jm lxxxj Swein bey Geẏſellwinde 
<del rend="strikethrough">habn </del> aufgehalten habt / Nu hat </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_349_r1l10">der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> vor vns cʒu den heẏligen behabt daʒ dıe ſein vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_349_r1l11"><expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>r</expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> ſein Alſo daʒ khein auſʒman vveder teil noch </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_349_r1l12">gemein daran <expan>hab
<del rend="strikethrough"><ex>e</ex>n</del></expan> <expan>Dar<ex>ümb</ex></expan> <expan>Ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan> / daʒ Jr dem <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan> <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex>m</expan> <expan>B<ex>urger</ex></expan> <expan>dıeſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_349_r1l13">ſeıne Swein wıder <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet Als etc das <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_349_r1l15">
<del rend="strikethrough"><expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ı </del> ın dıe <expan>ſ<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>ı</expan> Galli A xj<hi rend="sup">o</hi></ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_349" id="174r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab>Heincz von Gich czu Melsendorff </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, uns hat fürgelegt Heincz Spörlein,
                                <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger,</ex></expan> wie ir im lxxxi swein bey Geysellwinde
                        aufgehalten habt. Nu hat der <expan>eg<ex>enante</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> vor uns czu den heyligen behabt, daz die sein
                        und <expan>and<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> sein, also daz khein auszman weder teil noch
                        gemein daran <expan>hab</expan>. <expan>Dar<ex>umb</ex></expan>
<expan>ro<ex>gamus</ex></expan>, daz ir dem
                            <expan>eg<ex>enanten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan>
<expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan>
<expan>dieselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> seine swein wider
                            <expan>geb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wöllet. Als etc. Das
                                <expan>wölle<ex>n</ex></expan> etc. <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> in
                        die <expan>s<ex>an</ex>c<ex>t</ex>i</expan> Galli <expan>a<ex>nno</ex></expan> xi<hi rend="sup">o</hi>
</ab>
</div>
